snippet.title: Heroki - Teaser Trailer (2011)
snippet.description:
This is an old teaser trailer of a very early build of Heroki. Posted in 2011

Heroki is a young brave boy who's chosen to save his village high above the sky. In search of the stolen magic element from his village, Heroki embarks a great adventure through several worlds full of exploration and great challenges.
